Libcamera patches adding a sensor helper for the ov02c10 as well as some hackyadjusting of some global exposure constants. For some ungodly reason libcamera only has partial support for reading per-sensor yaml tuning so this is the easiest way for now. I'm working on a patch series to allow this tuning so we can fully upstream this cameras config. Feel free to adjust the constants below, I've played around for a bit and tried my best to understand how each algorithm works but if you find something better let me know.


Signed-off-by: Oliver <oliverjwhite07@gmail.com>

 src/ipa/libipa/camera_sensor_helper.cpp | 12 ++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 12 insertions(+)

